# [background arg="train_window_departing.png"]
leave --All--
join mcdonald 1
mcdonald: 没关系——

# [background arg="train_window_departing.png"]
leave --All--
join poirot 1
poirot: 你太客气了——

# [background arg="train_window_departing.png"]
leave --All--
